title: 11-month-old recovering after family dog bit baby several times
text:
An 11-month-old child is recovering—after suffering serious dog bites to the face—by the family dog on Saturday night.
Seattle fire officials say the child was taken to a hospital at around 6:00 p.m. Saturday.
The attack occurred at a home in North Seattle.
Neighbors said the dog always seemed to be well-behaved.
There is no word yet on the current condition of the child—or what will happen with the dog.
